text: import java.net.*; class TestProtocol { public static void main(String [] args ){ testProtocol ("http://www.dit.ie"); testProtocol ("https://www.dit.ie™); testProtocol ("ftp://dit.ie™); testProtocol ("mailto:aneel.rahim@dit.ie") ; } public static void testProtocol(String url) { try { URL u = new URL(url); System.out.println(u.getProtocol() + " is supported"); } catch (Exception ex) { System.out.println(url + " is not supported"); } } }
